profile: At Decimal we've completed hundreds of jobs; from tv mounts to full scale kitchen renovations. We'll walk you through the project, including how we'll execute and what the final product will look like. We're all about the details - none too small. Please let us know if you'd like references and we'd be happy to provide you with some. We're very excited to have been recruited to join HomeStars!
